  "commentary": "With SPX at 6819.57 in PIN regime and below the 6847 GEX flip, dealers are net long gamma and likely buying this dip while hedging short deltas, creating natural support. The massive positive gamma walls at 6850 (+4095.9M), 6875 (+3304.4M), and especially 6900 (+5613.8M) will act as strong resistance levels where dealers turn into sellers, while the 6700 level (-1397.5M negative gamma) provides a floor where dealer buying accelerates. Watch for mean reversion behavior with dealers stabilizing price action between these key levels.\n\nBottom line: expect a bounce toward 6850-6900 resistance with dealers providing support on dips.",
